{"tid":1825904,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【Now新聞台】美國密歇根州眾議院通過放寬持有使用電擊槍議案","createTime":"2020-01-15T16:42:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-15T17:52:01.000Z","uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1dec2d91e396778a9f263b419b26d11098a458a3","tid":1825904,"uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T16:42:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=376900\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D376900&d=8FzWv2H1QRiLw4sTAqHlBlKEWDR5zjN73Co06CeqttY%3D&h=8a224af9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D376900&h=bd7df06e\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=376900</a><br />\n【Now新聞台】美國密歇根州眾議院通過議案，容許十八歲或以上人士擁有及使用電擊槍。有反對議員和警方批評，新例可能對民眾構成危險。<br />\n<br />\n由共和黨控制的密歇根州眾議院，以84對24票通過議案，撤銷有關電擊槍的禁令，容許當地十八歲或以上人士，日後在毋須領取牌照或接受背景審查的情況下，銷售、擁有和「合理使用」電擊槍。密歇根州參議院稍後亦會討論和表決議案，預料在共和黨議員佔大多數情況下，亦會順利通過。<br />\n<br />\n密歇根州目前只是容許執法人員和廿一歲或以上、持有槍牌的人士使用電槍，而電槍和電擊槍是不同的，電槍是可以在十多呎範圍內遠距離使用，電擊槍就要直接接觸目標人物「埋身」使用。<br />\n<br />\n今次的議案發起人、共和黨州議員霍伊滕加歡迎議案獲通過，認為可以讓婦女選擇武器以外的方式自衛。<br />\n<br />\n不過有反對的議員批評，撤銷電擊槍禁令是不負責任。<br />\n當地警方亦關注法例一旦生效，一般未接受過適當訓練的市民都可以使用電擊槍，又指電擊槍是「埋身」使用，屆時有更大機會發生罪犯搶去電擊槍，再向受害人施襲的情況。"},{"pid":"1eec4599fd842233cb9057f182ede26dd5916377","tid":1825904,"uid":307619,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T16:42:51.000Z","msg":"( please forward to your English reading friends, colleagues, etc) <br />\n<br />\nMan arrested after taking picture of Hong Kong police in restaurant, with councillor decrying incident as &lsquo;arbitrary arrest&rsquo; | South China Morning Post<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.scmp.com/news/hong-kong/law-and-crime/article/3046100/man-arrested-after-catching-hong-kong-police-camera\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scmp.com%2Fnews%2Fhong-kong%2Flaw-and-crime%2Farticle%2F3046100%2Fman-arrested-after-catching-hong-kong-police-camera&d=8FzWv2H1QRiLw4sTAqHlBlKEWDR5zjN73Co06CeqttY%3D&h=0f4cb659\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.scmp.com/news/hong-kong/law-and-crime/article/3046100/man-arrested-after-catching-hong-kong-police-camera</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/65L3WEf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F65L3WEf.jpg&h=415440cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n蘋果日報A1頭條：影相都拉 青年警署被虐<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1824821\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1824821</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">至今仍未保釋<br />\n香港人今日唔出聲<br />\n呢種情況就會成為日常</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wKeoSjm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwKeoSjm.jpg&h=230579a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3cZ0Zw5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3cZ0Zw5.png&h=455277cc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2705dc6c5aab907b76187850c7dc8b7ca2c1d0f8","tid":1825904,"uid":92908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T17:47:29.000Z","msg":"係美國係電槍變成可以代替真槍<br />\n<br />\n港狗係兩樣一齊用"},{"pid":"aa27a382154284fe2f0d894994634dc153dd3914","tid":1825904,"uid":231583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2705dc6c5aab907b76187850c7dc8b7ca2c1d0f8","tid":1825904,"uid":92908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T17:47:29.000Z","msg":"係美國係電槍變成可以代替真槍<br />\n<br />\n港狗係兩樣一齊用"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T17:49:08.000Z","msg":"人地有民主制衡，香港有既係極權"},{"pid":"b3635e8d0bf8de5ad2ac68fda27726bcfec38ca3","tid":1825904,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T17:51:03.000Z","msg":"「當地警方亦關注法例一旦生效，一般未接受過適當訓練的市民都可以使用電擊槍，又指電擊槍是「埋身」使用，屆時有更大機會發生罪犯搶去電擊槍，再向受害人施襲的情況。」<br />\n<br />\nd罪犯一定唔會帶武器犯法啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1